    "body": "yes the coinbase needs to be explicitly set from now on. \nRelying on the order of accounts is discouraged (but at least they are correct now reflecting creation date of your keys). The new solution is backward compatible, so you can just use your first account as your coinbase if you used to do nothing.\n\n```\ngeth --etherbase 0x567fe258ab7c7c709034266cc6000832fffa --unlock 0 console 2>> geth.log\n```\n\nlet me know if you have issues.\n",
